                    "title": "Description"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "The unofficial successor to CyDown, Erika lets you download paid tweaks for free in Sileo, Saily, and Zebra!"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Features"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- Identical tweak database to CyDown \n- Includes a deb saver \n- Blocks the 'pirate repo bad' alert in Sileo \n- Pretty UI \n- Supports all modern package managers \n- Open source"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Instructions"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "1. Tap the icon at the top of the tweak you want to download \n2. Once the tweak has downloaded, tap on Get Zappy or go to /var/mobile/Media/Erika \n3. Install the deb"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Caveats"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- If a rootless deb doesn't exist on the server, it will download a rootful version as a fallback \n- 'Tweak not found on the server' is not a bug, it just means CyDown server doesn't yet have the tweak."
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
                },
                
